Package GalaxyDefenders

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Alien
    The Alien Class extends the Bug class.
    Bullet
    The Bullet class gives functionality to the bullets that are shot out by the sprite.
    GalaxyDefenders
    The GalaxyDefenders class runs a world that contains rows of aliens at the top of the screen and a sprite at the bottom of the screen.
    GalaxyDefendersWorld
    The GalaxyDefendersWorld class extends ActorWorld.
    JUGalaxyDefendersTest
    GalaxyDefenders tests: Sprite Alien Bullet PoweredBullet GalaxyDefendersWorld
    PoweredBullet
    The PoweredBullet class extends the Bullet class and acts as a power-up that clears the entire column of aliens.
    Sprite
    The Sprite class extends the Actor class.
